<plot>Amargi means "return to the womb" as well as "freedom". This is an experimental-type film with stylized images and frequent split screens that create a pleated structure of free associations and where visual sensations, illusions and the flow of sounds, like a web of music, freely mingle and intersect.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?033766</url></doc>
